name: Cybernotdienst.de - Phishing Expansion Pack v1
description:
The Expansion sets provides some basic indicator extraction and enrichment, as well ass  Spamassassin based pre-evaluation of emails. By running this playbook as part of the phishing investigation a decision can be made if a full investigation based on Palo Alto's Phishing Generic v3 is necessary or the incident can be closed as Spam.

The Content Pack includes widgets, Dasboards and Layouts.
